American Century Corp saidits Commerce Savings unit will sell 997,756 common shares inFirst American Financial Corp &lt;FAMR.O>, representing 18 pct ofFirst American.    The company said the shares are being repurchased by FirstAmerican for 29.4 mln dlrs and two real estate assets inCalifornia.    It said Commerce Savings acquired the shares in 1982 and1983. Reuter&#3;